Uses of Package
com.stremebase.map

  • Packages that use com.stremebase.map 
    Package Description
    com.stremebase.field
    com.stremebase.field offers some basic high-level fields to be used at the data access layer.
    com.stremebase.map
    com.stremebase.map contains all the low level maps that can be used when developing new custom fields.
  • Classes in com.stremebase.map used by com.stremebase.field 
    Class and Description
    ArrayMap
    A map that stores a fixed-size array of longs
    SetMap
    SetMap associates a key with a set or a bag of values.
    SetMap.SetEntry
    SetEntry contains not only key and value, but also an attribute for MULTISETs, the attribute is the count of values for ATTRIBUTEDSETs, you can assign any value but DB.NULL
    StackListMap
    A map for associating a dynamically expanding array of values with a key.
  • Classes in com.stremebase.map used by com.stremebase.map 
    Class and Description
    SetMap.SetEntry
    SetEntry contains not only key and value, but also an attribute for MULTISETs, the attribute is the count of values for ATTRIBUTEDSETs, you can assign any value but DB.NULL
